<section class="section section--compact" id="acct-small-business-disclosure">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="disclosure">
      <strong>TechBrot is an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm &mdash; not a CPA firm, and not Intuit.</strong> We keep your books accurate, reconciled, and reported in QuickBooks, and we coordinate with your CPA. <strong>Filing your income-tax return is a CPA&rsquo;s job</strong> &mdash; we don&rsquo;t file returns; we keep books a CPA can rely on and hand them over return-ready at tax time. For an Intuit account, login, subscription, or billing matter, Intuit&rsquo;s own support is the right path. QuickBooks and Intuit are registered trademarks of Intuit Inc.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

